This project took care of the following tasks:

1. Custom User Model -> with Production-ready permissions
2. Http-only cookies for access token and refresh token
3. User Registration, email confirmation
4. User Login/
5. Refresh Token for access token regeneration
6. User Logout
7. Reset Password via email confirmation
8. Change Password while logged in
9. Custom Token-Cookie-based authentication using JWT
10. Cors headers configuration
11. Simple react frontend with axios for API testing.
12. And more...
